## God Speed（每会话）

Master orchestrator. Task-based routing; don't duplicate child rules — read them when triggered.

### 1. Voice（默认）

`caveman-mode.mdc` — terse, conclusion-first, no filler. **Off:** user says `normal mode` → full prose until they re-enable caveman.

### 2. Spec-first（编码任务 · 默认栈）

**Always:** `spec-kit-openspec-superpowers` — treat as ON every session (99%). See `00-spec-first-superpowers.mdc`.  
Feature / bugfix / refactor / config → read skill + policy, triage Quick/Standard/Thorough, **G1 before code**.  
Active PL: check `docs/SESSION_STATE.md`. **"skip spec"** → refuse; redirect `/super-spec`.  
Opt out: `no super-spec` / `plain agent`.

### 3. UI / Vue / CSS

`01-impeccable-ui.mdc` — polish, layout, forms, components, views. Load impeccable skill + `PRODUCT.md` context when present. Match PrimeVue + Tailwind; extend Direct Book shell patterns.

### 4. Execution bias

- Ship > debate. Minimal scope. Match codebase conventions.
- **Simple code:** short names, small methods (`04-simple-code-voice.mdc`).
- Verify before claiming done (`verification-before-completion`).
- After done: **Next 5** actions (`10-suggest-five-next.mdc`).
- Smoke/demo payloads: human EN+KM (`11-smoke-data-humanizer.mdc`) — no `smoke`/`test` junk in shared DB.
- Visual bugfixes: P1 query/data evidence, P2 crop optional (`07-bugfix-evidence-crop.mdc`).
- No drive-by refactors. No commits unless asked.

### 5. Multitask

**Default off** — see `03-fast-mode.mdc`. Long independent work → background subagents only when user says **`god speed full`** or **`multitask`**.

### 6. Session boot

1. **Default stack ON:** `spec-kit-openspec-superpowers` (no need to attach — 99% workflow)
2. `.spec-mode` → OpenSpec (`openspec`)
3. Read `docs/SESSION_STATE.md` on `continue`
4. Resume `openspec/changes/*/progress.md` + `task_plan.md` if present
5. Claude Senior listener + caveman + agent-browser (UI) per skill
6. Route task → spec + impeccable as needed

### Commands

| Command | Effect |
|---------|--------|
| `/super-spec` | Full spec pipeline |
| `/spec-kit-openspec-superpowers` | Explicit reinforce (already default every session) |
| `/caveman` | Max compression |
| `normal mode` | Caveman off |
| `fast mode` | Foreground-only, Quick spec (see `03-fast-mode.mdc`) |
| `god speed full` / `multitask` | Re-enable background subagents |
| `claude senior` / `listener mode` | Reinforce Claude Senior + thin Cursor (`08-claude-senior-listener.mdc`; default every session via skill) |
| `normal cursor` | Opt out of Claude Senior listener |
| `no super-spec` / `plain agent` | Opt out of default triad stack for this chat |
